WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.750
Hey, good morning, family. After I did

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:05.789
my last video, I think the major thing

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:08.230
people wanted to know is, "Do you

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:11.870
have a pastor that is a

00:00:11.870 --> 00:00:11.880
female?"Folks,

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:14.990
let me tell you like

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.710
this: in Joel chapter 2, the Bible says

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.310
that in the last days, "I will pour out my

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:25.830
spirit upon your sons and your

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.029
daughters and on your

00:00:28.029 --> 00:00:28.039
handmaidens"—and

00:00:28.039 --> 00:00:30.910
that's a female.

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:34.110
So we're in those last days.

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:36.510
Regardless of whether you want to believe

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:39.950
that God can use a female or a male,

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.430
I'm here to say it's all hands

00:00:42.440 --> 00:00:43.590
on

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:46.310
deck. If the men are not going to do

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:48.510
the job and they're sitting back with

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:50.790
their thumb in their nose and

00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:52.389
being lazy, and the women

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:55.069
want to take the baton and say, "Hey, I

00:00:55.079 --> 00:00:57.189
know that God has called me for such a

00:00:57.199 --> 00:01:01.069
time as this to lead the people, to help

00:01:01.079 --> 00:01:03.189
bring prayer

00:01:03.189 --> 00:01:03.199
in,"that's

00:01:03.199 --> 00:01:06.390
where I'm at. If I see the

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:09.109
anointing and the presence of God

00:01:09.119 --> 00:01:12.190
on male or female, I'm going to follow

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.590
and listen to what they have to say just

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:16.830
because of what Joel chapter 2:28 said:

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:20.270
"And it shall come to pass

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:22.710
afterward that I will pour out my spirit

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.749
upon all flesh; your sons

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:28.390
and your daughters shall prophesy, your

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.870
old men shall dream dreams, your

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:34.030
young men shall see visions. And also

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:36.910
upon the servants and upon the handmaids

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:39.429
in those days will I pour out my

00:01:39.429 --> 00:01:39.439
spirit."So

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:42.389
you see

00:01:42.399 --> 00:01:44.789
what the word is saying right there?

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:47.429
That's what I go by. I know Paul talks

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:49.270
about having women be silent in the

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.910
church and not interrupting,

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:55.190
but I believe as we draw closer

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:58.029
to the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ,

00:01:58.039 --> 00:02:01.069
we are seeing God put His hand of

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:04.630
fire even on His sons, His daughters,

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:07.950
and on the handmaidens. I

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.229
believe that's what we're seeing right

00:02:09.239 --> 00:02:12.390
now. We can criticize and say, "Well,

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:13.949
they shouldn't be in this; women

00:02:13.959 --> 00:02:15.550
shouldn't do this; women shouldn't do

00:02:15.550 --> 00:02:15.560
that,"but

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.190
I'm going by Joel chapter

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:20.670
2 in the Old Testament. Then

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:23.229
we have Acts chapter 2, which says this is

00:02:23.239 --> 00:02:26.390
that which was spoken by the prophet Joel.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.229
The Holy Ghost and fire came into the

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.309
upper room and filled them all with

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:32.710
tongues of fire, and the women and the

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.070
men were speaking with tongues of fire,

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:37.110
and the glory of the Lord filled that

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:40.509
whole place like a mighty rushing wind.

00:02:40.519 --> 00:02:45.470
So I know what the Lord has shown me

00:02:45.470 --> 00:02:45.480
concerning

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:48.630
these last days. From Kathryn

00:02:48.630 --> 00:02:48.640
Kuhlman

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:52.149
to Joyce Meyer to the people

00:02:52.159 --> 00:02:53.670
that have ministered to

00:02:53.670 --> 00:02:53.680
me—she

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.430
talks about the "Battlefield of the

00:02:55.430 --> 00:02:55.440
Mind"and

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:57.309
some amazing

00:02:57.319 --> 00:03:01.190
things she went

00:03:01.190 --> 00:03:01.200
through—I

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:04.830
look at the people that God

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:08.509
is calling up right now. Like I said,

00:03:08.519 --> 00:03:10.589
ladies and gentlemen, it's all hands on

00:03:10.599 --> 00:03:13.270
deck. We have a lot of men that do not

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:16.550
have a backbone like a crowbar,

00:03:16.550 --> 00:03:16.560
who

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:19.390
are being limp-wristed, wearing skinny

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:21.589
jeans and using fog machines, wanting to follow the

00:03:21.589 --> 00:03:21.599
crowd—kind

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:23.949
of men that don't even know

00:03:23.959 --> 00:03:25.550
they're metrosexual, that don't even know

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:29.190
who they are. I identify myself as a

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:32.990
man or a woman—or, "Oh, I identify

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.110
myself as a dog."I heard that

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:36.869
kids in

00:03:36.879 --> 00:03:38.910
these schools were coming to school

00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:41.789
saying that they identify as a dog or a

00:03:41.799 --> 00:03:44.509
cat, and they dress up like a dog or a

00:03:44.519 --> 00:03:47.229
cat before they come to school.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.670
Folks, we don't even know what we

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:53.789
are anymore. So God's trying to find

00:03:53.799 --> 00:03:57.110
somebody that will just say yes without

00:03:57.120 --> 00:04:00.149
all this religious stuff going,

00:04:00.159 --> 00:04:01.789
"Well, you know, they can't be used because

00:04:01.799 --> 00:04:04.309
of their parts."God's saying, "I'm looking

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:07.229
for a pure heart,"and I can't find one

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:08.550
because right now we've got a bunch of

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:09.910
knuckleheads that don't even know who

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.270
they are anymore. I'm not

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.869
going to sit here and criticize and go,

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:17.270
"Well, she can't go up there and

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:19.670
lead prayer because she's a

00:04:19.670 --> 00:04:19.680
female."Folks,

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:22.069
you're thinking too

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:23.870
small for what God's trying to do in

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:26.350
these last days. God said, "I will pour

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:30.189
out my spirit upon all

00:04:30.189 --> 00:04:30.199
flesh."So

00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:32.870
that's what I'm looking for. If

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:35.270
you want to rock in your chair and sit

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.350
there and criticize everybody who's

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:40.110
trying to do something good for God, then

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.590
you probably shouldn't watch my channel.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.670
I believe my wife is called; she's my

00:04:47.670 --> 00:04:47.680
rearguard,

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:49.749
my helper, and my

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:51.310
friend. I've seen an

00:04:51.320 --> 00:04:55.029
anointing on her: she dreams,

00:04:55.039 --> 00:04:57.469
she has visions, she sees things,

00:04:57.479 --> 00:04:59.350
and God uses her just as much as He

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:01.710
uses me. Yeah, I'm the head of the

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:04.550
house, I run our home,

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:06.270
I flow with the spirit of the Lord,

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:09.029
and I lead my family, but I

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:10.870
believe she's my helpmate and she's my

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:13.870
friend, and she's here

00:05:13.880 --> 00:05:15.749
to teach just as much as me.

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:18.150
This channel is just not my

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:19.590
own; He said, "I've called her to walk

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:21.430
beside you, not behind you, Brandon."There

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:21.440
are

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.790
people that get all

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:25.590
upset about that and say, "Well, women

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.189
shouldn't do that,"but I'm here to tell

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:29.790
you you're wrong because I believe with

00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:31.870
all my heart it's all hands on deck. We

00:05:31.870 --> 00:05:31.880
saw

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:33.950
that in scripture right here, Joel

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:36.110
chapter 2, right here in black and

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:40.270
white. In the last days He said, "I'll pour

00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:41.909
my spirit upon all

00:05:41.909 --> 00:05:41.919
flesh."So

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:45.270
we're going to go with that

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.629
because Joel prophesied it, and then we

00:05:47.639 --> 00:05:50.390
see in Acts chapter 2 that this is that which

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.909
was spoken by the prophet Joel: "In the

00:05:52.919 --> 00:05:55.390
last days I will pour out my spirit upon

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:59.189
all

00:05:59.189 --> 00:05:59.199
flesh."We're

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:01.150
seeing that already, and

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:04.270
that was 2,000 years ago. So

00:06:04.280 --> 00:06:06.870
here we are right now in present day, and

00:06:06.880 --> 00:06:09.990
the Lord tells us, "Brandon, I'm going to

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:14.070
do one last call, one major push for a

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:16.589
harvest of

00:06:16.599 --> 00:06:20.070
souls. Will you be a part of it? I'm just

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:23.990
looking for someone

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:24.000
who

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:27.510
will just say yes, son, who will help

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:31.150
me bring in the

00:06:31.150 --> 00:06:31.160
harvest."I'm

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.150
saying it from the mountaintops that

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:36.150
Jesus Christ is

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:38.990
coming. The eyes of the Lord are running

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:40.670
to and fro throughout the whole earth,

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:42.270
looking for a heart who's perfect

00:06:42.280 --> 00:06:43.309
towards

00:06:43.319 --> 00:06:46.950
Him, looking for someone that will have a

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:51.189
great yielded want-to to say, "Hey God,

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:56.150
here am I, send me."Send me

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:59.029
to the nations to preach, to teach, to do

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:04.390
whatever it takes to bring in the

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.230
lost. I

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:10.150
refuse to let the rocks do my

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:13.550
job, for it says in the word that if I

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:17.230
don't praise Him, the rocks will cry

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:20.909
out. I'm telling you, God is a God

00:07:20.919 --> 00:07:23.909
that's worthy to be praised, and I refuse

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:26.830
to let the rocks do my

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:30.469
job. I will praise Him today because He

00:07:30.479 --> 00:07:33.350
is worthy to be praised. Last night at

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:36.469
Wednesday night church, the glory came

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:39.990
down and the presence of the Lord was so

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.990
strong you could feel

00:07:41.990 --> 00:07:42.000
it.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.469
Whenever you go into a church

00:07:47.639 --> 00:07:50.230
service and it

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.550
keeps going and going, and

00:07:57.479 --> 00:08:02.510
you lose track of time in the

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:05.270
glory because everything your

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.990
spirit

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:10.469
ever needs is at His

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:13.670
feet, people go,

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:18.230
"Well, what time am I going home?"If you

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:20.990
don't want to sit at His feet, give me

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:22.909
the keys and the code and I'll lock up

00:08:22.919 --> 00:08:24.270
your building for

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:27.230
you,

00:08:27.230 --> 00:08:27.240
because

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:28.950
nothing else

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:31.629
matters to me. There's nothing in

00:08:31.639 --> 00:08:34.670
this earth that I want more than to sit

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:37.029
at His

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:40.070
feet. You can lose yourself in the

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:42.589
numbers and the

00:08:42.599 --> 00:08:44.790
money because it's

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:48.150
what the flesh wants, but

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:51.790
as for me and my house, we will serve the

00:08:51.800 --> 00:08:55.389
Lord with all our hearts, all our minds,

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:58.550
all our soul, and all our strength, and

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:00.790
we'll love our neighbor as ourselves. We'll

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:02.310
love those because those two

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:05.509
angels that stood over my bed that night

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:09.590
said, to make

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.190
a long story

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.949
short, what he needs to know is that when he

00:09:13.959 --> 00:09:16.509
stands before the Father, what he will be

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:18.590
judged upon the most is what

00:09:18.590 --> 00:09:18.600
he

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:20.430
did

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:23.750
with love. How did he love his brother?

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:26.470
How did he love those around him and

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:28.550
treat people with respect and honor?

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:33.430
What did he do with love beyond anything

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:35.150
else? It won't be

00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:36.870
because I gave this amount of

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:38.710
money or I did this.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:41.230
No, how did you walk in love

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:43.990
towards your

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.910
brethren? Love takes no account of a

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:49.030
suffered wrong, ladies and gentlemen. In

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:52.230
the comment section, love takes no

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.829
account of a suffered wrong—even to a

00:09:53.839 --> 00:09:55.509
preacher who's talking trash about you

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:58.710
behind your back.

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:06.030
I choose to love. I choose to

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:08.750
be what Jesus has called me to be in

00:10:08.760 --> 00:10:11.509
this earth.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:18.470
I stay

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:22.790
vertical; I refuse to go horizontal. I go

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:25.150
vertical regardless of people cursing

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:26.790
you with their mouth or regardless of

00:10:26.800 --> 00:10:29.030
people coming on here from the

00:10:29.030 --> 00:10:29.040
occult.

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:31.949
It's

00:10:31.959 --> 00:10:36.629
in Him I move and have my being.

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:40.509
He is the one I'm after.

00:10:40.519 --> 00:10:42.870
Some of

00:10:42.880 --> 00:10:45.910
you are just after what you can get

00:10:45.920 --> 00:10:48.990
on this earth, but everything you achieve,

00:10:50.639 --> 00:10:56.030
unless it's for

00:10:56.040 --> 00:10:59.629
Him, it will burn up like chaff before

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:00.670
His

00:11:00.680 --> 00:11:04.590
throne. It will either be pure like

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:08.829
gold that will stand the fire, or it will

00:11:08.839 --> 00:11:10.350
be straw and

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:12.829
stubble.

00:11:19.839 --> 00:11:24.069
I choose to not lay up my treasures

00:11:24.079 --> 00:11:28.110
upon this earth because all I know is

00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:30.790
that when I get on the other side, He's

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:34.430
either going to say, "I knew you,"or "Depart

00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:36.069
from me; I never knew

00:11:36.069 --> 00:11:36.079
you."I

00:11:36.079 --> 00:11:39.069
heard Benny

00:11:39.079 --> 00:11:42.430
Hinn say he was on the

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:45.870
table having that heart attack

00:11:45.880 --> 00:11:47.949
and he was in line to go before the Father.

00:11:47.949 --> 00:11:47.959
An organist

00:11:47.959 --> 00:11:49.790
was playing,

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:51.509
and Jesus was standing there

00:11:51.519 --> 00:11:54.269
greeting the people.

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:56.870
She would play a certain sound, and the

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:58.910
sound was either a welcoming sound or a

00:11:58.920 --> 00:12:02.350
sound of judgment. Either Jesus gave

00:12:02.360 --> 00:12:08.069
you a nod of

00:12:08.069 --> 00:12:08.079
"yes"or

00:12:08.079 --> 00:12:09.870
"no."As Benny

00:12:09.870 --> 00:12:09.880
Hinn

00:12:09.880 --> 00:12:13.750
got before

00:12:13.760 --> 00:12:17.069
the Father, he saw all his

00:12:17.069 --> 00:12:17.079
works—the

00:12:17.079 --> 00:12:19.069
healing

00:12:19.079 --> 00:12:22.269
revivals, the souls that had come

00:12:22.269 --> 00:12:22.279
in—but

00:12:22.279 --> 00:12:25.110
over the course of time his heart had

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:27.470
become cold to the Father. The Lord

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:29.949
showed me and He showed my wife, Diana,

00:12:29.959 --> 00:12:32.430
"Brandon, I'll use whoever I want to.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:34.030
Just because you have the anointing and

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:35.189
just because you flow under the

00:12:35.199 --> 00:12:37.750
anointing doesn't mean that I know

00:12:37.750 --> 00:12:37.760
you."I

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:41.189
will use whoever I want. The anointing is

00:12:41.199 --> 00:12:43.590
not about

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:45.990
relationship; the anointing is a

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:48.629
tool. We qualify for the anointing,

00:12:48.639 --> 00:12:50.069
but He doesn't turn

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:53.389
it off because it's a tool,

00:12:53.399 --> 00:12:55.350
just like this shirt

00:12:55.350 --> 00:12:55.360
covers

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:58.030
me

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:02.949
or my shaver shaves my head.

00:13:02.959 --> 00:13:05.790
The anointing is a

00:13:05.800 --> 00:13:08.590
cloak

00:13:08.590 --> 00:13:08.600
that

00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:11.269
helps

00:13:11.279 --> 00:13:14.389
us to operate in this earth so that

00:13:14.399 --> 00:13:16.670
we're able to get the job done. Does that

00:13:16.680 --> 00:13:17.990
make sense?

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:22.389
We are the tool, but

00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:24.430
we are the glove.

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:25.710
The Holy

00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:28.389
Spirit said, "You are the glove; I am the

00:13:28.399 --> 00:13:30.470
hand that goes in the glove. You are

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:32.470
always to deflect the glory to the

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:34.990
Father."So

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:36.629
that's where we are right now. In these

00:13:36.639 --> 00:13:39.550
end times, it's all hands on deck, but

00:13:39.560 --> 00:13:41.310
just because you have some

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:43.189
anointing

00:13:43.199 --> 00:13:45.829
doesn't mean that He's intimate

00:13:45.839 --> 00:13:49.750
with you. Intimacy is sitting at His feet

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:52.230
on a daily

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:55.629
basis. "Hello, Father, how are

00:13:55.629 --> 00:13:55.639
you?"Don't

00:13:55.639 --> 00:13:59.389
lose yourself

00:13:59.399 --> 00:14:04.310
in works, numbers, growth, or money. Lose yourself

00:14:11.399 --> 00:14:16.069
in His

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:19.629
breath. "Father, I need

00:14:19.639 --> 00:14:23.189
You; Father, I worship

00:14:23.199 --> 00:14:27.150
You. I want

00:14:27.160 --> 00:14:29.310
to have a revelation knowledge according

00:14:29.320 --> 00:14:31.990
to Ephesians, that the eyes of my

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.189
understanding would be enlightened

00:14:34.189 --> 00:14:34.199
today."I

00:14:34.199 --> 00:14:37.350
thank You, Lord, that I sit

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:38.389
at Your

00:14:38.399 --> 00:14:41.230
feet. When I sit before You in

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:43.910
that day, He either

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:54.069
says, "Brandon, I knew

00:14:54.069 --> 00:14:54.079
you,"or

00:14:54.079 --> 00:14:55.829
"You did a lot on the earth, but I never

00:14:55.839 --> 00:14:58.590
had a relationship with you."Diana is going

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:00.629
to read this to you because it's

00:15:00.639 --> 00:15:02.550
very important that you

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:04.030
understand.

00:15:04.040 --> 00:15:06.670
Oh, it's just about grace, brother?

00:15:06.680 --> 00:15:10.030
Yeah,

00:15:10.040 --> 00:15:13.430
you're saved by

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:16.590
grace through faith, not of works, lest any

00:15:16.600 --> 00:15:19.990
man should boast; it is a gift of God. We

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:21.550
understand that, but it's about

00:15:21.560 --> 00:15:23.749
relationship. I want you to meditate on

00:15:23.759 --> 00:15:26.069
this scripture while I'm trying to

00:15:26.079 --> 00:15:29.389
bring

00:15:29.399 --> 00:15:31.389
you to a conclusion of all the things

00:15:31.399 --> 00:15:34.710
that you think make you

00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:38.629
qualified.

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:47.430
I'm

00:15:47.440 --> 00:15:49.910
taking it all back to a

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:50.990
heart

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:53.590
thing.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:59.550
Holy

00:15:59.560 --> 00:16:02.389
Communion is holy, but it is an act of

00:16:02.399 --> 00:16:04.150
worship in my

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:08.710
house. It's an act of, "God, I love You; I

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:11.629
just want to be at Your feet. I just want

00:16:11.639 --> 00:16:14.949
to know You

00:16:17.990 --> 00:16:18.000
more."I

00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:24.110
just want a

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:27.030
personal relationship with the Lord

00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:28.749
Jesus Christ.

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:34.870
Matthew

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:38.350
7:21: "Not everyone that saith unto me,

00:16:38.360 --> 00:16:40.389
Lord, Lord, shall enter into the kingdom

00:16:40.399 --> 00:16:43.150
of heaven; but he that doeth the will of

00:16:43.160 --> 00:16:45.670
my Father which is in heaven. Many will

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:48.990
say to me in that day, Lord, Lord, have we

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:51.790
not prophesied in thy name? And in thy

00:16:51.800 --> 00:16:54.870
name have cast out devils? And in thy

00:16:54.880 --> 00:16:57.430
name done many wonderful works? And then

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:59.790
will I profess unto them, I never knew

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:03.270
you: depart from me, ye that work

00:17:03.270 --> 00:17:03.280
iniquity."I

00:17:03.280 --> 00:17:05.390
don't want Him saying that to

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:08.549
me.

00:17:14.160 --> 00:17:18.230
It

00:17:18.240 --> 00:17:22.909
takes some anointing to cast out a devil

00:17:22.909 --> 00:17:22.919
or

00:17:22.919 --> 00:17:25.949
raise the

00:17:25.959 --> 00:17:28.909
dead,

00:17:40.840 --> 00:17:43.470
but He said, "Depart from me; I

00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:46.830
never knew you."What is it about?

00:17:46.840 --> 00:17:49.870
It's about relationship. It's about

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:53.190
sitting at His feet and saying,

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:56.149
"Jesus, I love

00:17:56.149 --> 00:17:56.159
You."Communion

00:17:56.159 --> 00:18:00.270
with Him—a heart thing. For the eyes of

00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:01.789
the Lord are running to and fro

00:18:01.799 --> 00:18:03.789
throughout the whole earth, looking for a

00:18:03.799 --> 00:18:06.110
heart who's perfect toward

00:18:06.120 --> 00:18:08.789
Him. I

00:18:08.799 --> 00:18:11.870
pray, "Father, if Your eyes

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:14.029
are roaming right now,

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:19.270
help my heart to be what pleases You

00:18:19.270 --> 00:18:19.280
today."Help

00:18:19.280 --> 00:18:22.390
my heart, Father, to be

00:18:22.400 --> 00:18:24.149
somebody that You're

00:18:24.159 --> 00:18:26.350
able to rest on. At my

00:18:26.360 --> 00:18:29.630
house, I make this

00:18:29.640 --> 00:18:32.149
house a place that He would be

00:18:32.159 --> 00:18:34.630
comfortable coming to. If He was to

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:37.630
manifest in real form and

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.590
knock on the door,

00:18:39.600 --> 00:18:41.710
would He open your door and look

00:18:41.720 --> 00:18:44.270
around and go, "Man, there's a lot of sin

00:18:44.280 --> 00:18:47.149
in

00:18:47.159 --> 00:18:48.549
here,"or

00:18:48.559 --> 00:18:51.070
does He open your door

00:18:51.080 --> 00:18:54.190
and go, "I can come in here

00:18:55.440 --> 00:18:58.029
and have a glass

00:18:58.039 --> 00:19:00.270
of iced tea with Brandon because I feel

00:19:00.280 --> 00:19:03.110
comfortable"?

00:19:11.919 --> 00:19:15.789
Ladies and gentlemen,

00:19:15.799 --> 00:19:18.669
practice His

00:19:18.679 --> 00:19:22.230
presence. Father, I don't want

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:24.230
anything to come through these

00:19:24.230 --> 00:19:24.240
eye

00:19:24.240 --> 00:19:26.230
gates

00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:28.549
that will offend You. Take captive of

00:19:28.559 --> 00:19:30.510
your thoughts.

00:19:30.520 --> 00:19:32.510
Men, don't be going around

00:19:32.520 --> 00:19:35.230
church lusting after women.

00:19:35.230 --> 00:19:35.240
You've

00:19:35.240 --> 00:19:38.470
got to

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:41.590
have your eye gates and your mind pure before the

00:19:41.600 --> 00:19:44.669
Father.

00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:52.029
He can hear your thoughts. If

00:19:52.029 --> 00:19:52.039
you have

00:19:52.039 --> 00:19:53.789
thoughts that

00:19:53.799 --> 00:19:56.669
are bad,

00:19:56.679 --> 00:19:59.430
He'll say,

00:19:59.440 --> 00:20:02.190
"Brandon, check your

00:20:02.190 --> 00:20:02.200
thoughts."Why?

00:20:02.200 --> 00:20:04.789
Because it's

00:20:04.799 --> 00:20:07.710
offensive.

00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:19.390
We're not perfect,

00:20:19.400 --> 00:20:21.390
but

00:20:21.400 --> 00:20:26.430
I'm trying

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:30.430
to challenge you to come up

00:20:30.440 --> 00:20:32.950
higher. Diana and I have

00:20:38.559 --> 00:20:40.070
got our stuff we're going through

00:20:40.080 --> 00:20:42.549
just like everybody else, but it's the

00:20:42.559 --> 00:20:45.390
heart that is quick to repent and

00:20:45.400 --> 00:20:47.590
says, "Father, I need

00:20:50.990 --> 00:20:51.000
You."Stop

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:56.310
trying to

00:20:56.320 --> 00:21:00.230
box God in and being so small-minded that

00:21:00.240 --> 00:21:02.270
you think He has to operate in the

00:21:02.280 --> 00:21:04.830
way you think He's going to operate.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:16.230
God loves you and He wants

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:18.950
relationship with you.

00:21:24.520 --> 00:21:27.390
He said, "Brandon, tell them to come

00:21:27.400 --> 00:21:29.830
unto

00:21:29.830 --> 00:21:29.840
me."Matthew:

00:21:29.840 --> 00:21:33.149
"Come to me, all you who are weary

00:21:33.159 --> 00:21:35.510
and burdened, and I will give you rest.

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:37.830
Take my yoke upon you and learn from me,

00:21:37.840 --> 00:21:40.310
for I am gentle and humble in heart, and

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:43.789
you will find rest for your souls. For my

00:21:43.799 --> 00:21:46.789
yoke is easy and my burden is

00:21:56.990 --> 00:21:57.000
light."Run

00:22:04.760 --> 00:22:08.350
to God when you sin; don't run from

00:22:08.360 --> 00:22:11.350
Him. Your sin is none of the devil's

00:22:11.360 --> 00:22:14.310
business. I come to Him with communion

00:22:14.320 --> 00:22:17.350
when I sin and say, "Father, at Your

00:22:17.360 --> 00:22:20.110
mercy seat,

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:29.430
I bow myself in humility

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:33.390
and say, Father, use me. Forgive

00:22:33.400 --> 00:22:36.830
me; wash me in Your blood; cleanse me from

00:22:36.840 --> 00:22:37.590
all

00:22:45.630 --> 00:22:45.640
unrighteousness."The

00:22:51.480 --> 00:22:53.909
sin issue is already taken

00:22:53.919 --> 00:22:55.830
care of. He said

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:58.950
if you confess your sins, He is

00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:01.190
faithful and just to forgive you

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:05.070
of your sins and cleanse you from all

00:23:05.080 --> 00:23:06.750
unrighteousness.

00:23:06.760 --> 00:23:09.350
So

00:23:18.600 --> 00:23:21.830
I seek Him daily. I

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:25.350
just

00:23:25.360 --> 00:23:28.710
felt it in my heart to

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:30.669
spur you to have an intimate

00:23:30.679 --> 00:23:32.510
relationship with Him.

00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:38.510
Does He know

00:23:38.520 --> 00:23:41.510
you?

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:57.549
My wife

00:23:57.559 --> 00:24:00.310
knows me; my kids know me.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:14.710
Do you look at Him as

00:24:14.720 --> 00:24:17.269
some kind of religious,

00:24:17.269 --> 00:24:17.279
far-out

00:24:17.279 --> 00:24:19.470
thing?

00:24:19.470 --> 00:24:19.480
You've

00:24:19.480 --> 00:24:22.269
got to take down that

00:24:22.279 --> 00:24:26.149
wall. "Come unto me and I will give you

00:24:34.230 --> 00:24:34.240
rest."Lean

00:24:43.279 --> 00:24:46.430
into Him.

00:25:04.919 --> 00:25:07.470
Trust, lean

00:25:07.480 --> 00:25:10.190
on, rely on, and be confident in the Lord.

00:25:18.399 --> 00:25:20.510
Delight yourself also in the Lord, and He

00:25:20.520 --> 00:25:22.350
will give you the desires and secret

00:25:22.360 --> 00:25:24.630
petitions of your heart. Commit your way

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:27.870
to the Lord; trust, lean on, rely on, and be

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:29.669
confident also in Him, and He will bring

00:25:29.679 --> 00:25:34.990
it to pass.

00:25:46.320 --> 00:25:48.029
That's intimacy right there.

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:17.190
Abraham staggered not

00:26:17.200 --> 00:26:19.190
at the promise of God through unbelief,

00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:21.669
but was strong in faith, giving glory to

00:26:21.679 --> 00:26:25.110
God. He was fully persuaded—that

00:26:25.110 --> 00:26:25.120
is confidence—that

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:27.590
what God had promised, He

00:26:27.590 --> 00:26:27.600
was

00:26:27.600 --> 00:26:30.590
able also to perform.

00:26:39.799 --> 00:26:42.870
I'm not moved by what I see

00:26:42.870 --> 00:26:42.880
or

00:26:42.880 --> 00:26:45.909
hear; I'm only

00:26:45.919 --> 00:26:47.950
moved by what the word of God

00:26:47.960 --> 00:26:52.870
says.

00:26:54.559 --> 00:26:58.870
Jesus Christ,

00:26:58.880 --> 00:26:59.750
the

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:03.549
same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:27:03.559 --> 00:27:06.310
If He did it

00:27:06.320 --> 00:27:09.149
2,000 years ago, He's still doing it

00:27:09.159 --> 00:27:11.990
today. He's still healing

00:27:11.990 --> 00:27:12.000
and

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:14.470
delivering.

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:16.710
He gave us the authority to cast out

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:19.230
devils and lay

00:27:19.240 --> 00:27:21.269
hands on the sick.

00:27:26.279 --> 00:27:28.590
We have got to come up higher in

00:27:28.600 --> 00:27:31.510
our thinking

00:27:31.520 --> 00:27:34.990
and say, "Father,

00:27:35.000 --> 00:27:37.070
I

00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:39.909
want more of You.

00:27:39.919 --> 00:27:41.710
I want more revelation of

00:27:41.720 --> 00:27:44.590
who You are in

00:27:50.399 --> 00:27:52.950
me."Abraham

00:27:58.399 --> 00:28:02.789
was a friend of God. I

00:28:02.799 --> 00:28:04.630
want Him to call me

00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:07.990
friend. "I am a friend of God.

00:28:13.080 --> 00:28:18.190
He calls me friend."Think about it.

00:28:18.200 --> 00:28:22.509
Who am I that You are mindful of

00:28:22.519 --> 00:28:28.590
me? That You hear me when I call?

00:28:28.600 --> 00:28:33.789
Is it true that You are thinking of me?

00:28:33.799 --> 00:28:37.990
Oh, how You love me. It's

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:40.789
amazing.

00:28:40.799 --> 00:28:44.269
I am a friend of

00:28:44.279 --> 00:28:47.590
God.

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:59.870
Does He call you friend today?

00:29:11.399 --> 00:29:14.430
My heart is for

00:29:14.440 --> 00:29:16.990
Him. Search me and know

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:19.110
me

00:29:19.120 --> 00:29:23.149
today. Create in me a clean heart,

00:29:23.149 --> 00:29:23.159
O

00:29:23.159 --> 00:29:25.789
God. You are the

00:29:25.799 --> 00:29:28.190
potter; I am the clay.

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:32.630
Help us not to get so stuck on

00:29:32.640 --> 00:29:35.950
these religious things.

00:29:37.880 --> 00:29:40.590
I

00:29:40.600 --> 00:29:44.149
want everything to do with

00:29:44.159 --> 00:29:46.710
relationship. Father, we lift up this body

00:29:46.720 --> 00:29:49.509
before You and we thank You

00:29:49.519 --> 00:29:50.750
that You were wounded for our

00:29:50.760 --> 00:29:52.630
transgressions, You were bruised for our

00:29:52.640 --> 00:29:55.110
iniquities, the chastisement of our peace

00:29:55.120 --> 00:29:58.029
was upon You, and with Your stripes, Lord,

00:29:58.039 --> 00:29:59.269
we are

00:29:59.279 --> 00:30:02.110
healed.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:04.789
We thank You that we don't have

00:30:04.799 --> 00:30:08.110
to be broke, busted, and disgusted anymore.

00:30:19.320 --> 00:30:21.710
We take this by faith and we

00:30:21.720 --> 00:30:25.470
are fully persuaded that Jesus Christ is

00:30:25.480 --> 00:30:28.909
our healer and our deliverer.

00:30:38.559 --> 00:30:41.190
Now, Lord, we take the

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:44.590
blood and we apply the blood of

00:30:44.600 --> 00:30:48.110
Jesus over our children, my wife,

00:30:48.110 --> 00:30:48.120
and

00:30:48.120 --> 00:30:49.269
our

00:30:49.279 --> 00:30:53.909
finances.

00:30:59.559 --> 00:31:02.029
Forgive us, Father, of our

00:31:02.039 --> 00:31:05.269
sins. We enter in by the blood of the

00:31:05.279 --> 00:31:08.070
Lamb. We

00:31:16.279 --> 00:31:21.669
plead the blood of Jesus

00:31:21.679 --> 00:31:26.070
in the courts of heaven. When we mess up

00:31:26.070 --> 00:31:26.080
or

00:31:26.080 --> 00:31:29.389
stumble,

00:31:29.399 --> 00:31:33.190
we call out for the blood.

00:31:36.279 --> 00:31:42.230
It will never lose its

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:47.190
power.

00:31:53.159 --> 00:31:55.470
Father,

00:31:55.480 --> 00:31:58.149
I

00:31:58.159 --> 00:32:00.389
apply it to our home. I

00:32:00.389 --> 00:32:00.399
plead

00:32:00.399 --> 00:32:02.310
the

00:32:02.320 --> 00:32:07.750
blood.

00:32:10.880 --> 00:32:16.830
Lord, You're

00:32:16.840 --> 00:32:19.710
beautiful; Your

00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:22.029
face is

00:32:22.039 --> 00:32:29.190
all I seek.

00:32:29.200 --> 00:32:30.909
And

00:32:30.919 --> 00:32:33.430
when Your

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:35.990
eyes are

00:32:36.000 --> 00:32:39.629
on this

00:32:39.639 --> 00:32:42.710
child, Your

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:44.909
grace

00:32:44.919 --> 00:32:50.389
abounds to

00:32:50.399 --> 00:32:51.990
me.

00:34:05.279 --> 00:34:12.750
Jesus, what a wonder You

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:17.710
are. You are so

00:34:17.720 --> 00:34:23.389
gentle, so pure, and so

00:34:23.399 --> 00:34:25.069
kind.

00:34:25.079 --> 00:34:29.310
You shine

00:34:29.320 --> 00:34:34.310
like a bright morning

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:37.090
star.

00:34:49.599 --> 00:34:55.669
Jesus, You're the sweetest name of

00:34:55.679 --> 00:34:58.390
all.

00:34:58.400 --> 00:35:03.470
You always hear me when I

00:35:03.480 --> 00:35:05.790
call;

00:35:05.800 --> 00:35:11.030
You lift me up each time I fall.

00:36:38.040 --> 00:36:41.230
Your name is like

