01:02:28.160 --> 01:02:30.589
President Trump for special covering.

01:02:35.440 --> 01:02:37.910
Cover his mind

01:02:37.910 --> 01:02:37.920
and

01:02:37.920 --> 01:02:39.309
body. Thank You for

01:02:39.319 --> 01:02:41.230
President Trump

01:02:41.230 --> 01:02:41.240
today—that

01:02:41.240 --> 01:02:44.309
he will release the

01:02:46.960 --> 01:02:48.230
wealth from the

01:02:48.240 --> 01:02:51.309
deep

01:02:51.319 --> 01:02:53.670
for the body of Christ.

01:03:05.000 --> 01:03:07.190
Put a smile on your

01:03:07.200 --> 01:03:09.589
